org.datavec.api.transform.metadata

Interface ColumnMetaData

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseColumnMetaData, BinaryMetaData, BooleanMetaData, CategoricalMetaData, DoubleMetaData, FloatMetaData, IntegerMetaData, LongMetaData, NDArrayMetaData, StringMetaData, TimeMetaData

    public interface ColumnMetaData
extends java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    ColumnMetaData: metadata for each column. Used to define: (a) the type of each column, and (b) any restrictions on the allowable values in each column
